      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Affordable & Road-Ready \u2014 A Solid Value Pick! \ud83d\ude97 Looking for dependable transportation without breaking the bank? This vehicle runs and drives, making it a practical choice for budget-conscious buyers! The exterior shows some wear and cosmetic blemishes consistent with its age and use \u2014 nothing hidden here. The interior is functional with signs of everyday use, and mechanically it gets the job done. Priced fairly to reflect its condition, this is a great opportunity for someone who needs reliable wheels at an honest price. Come take a look \u2014 what you see is what you get! \ud83d\udd11",
