    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture before you consider making a purchase. The exterior shows visible wear consistent with regular use \u2014 you'll notice some scratches, minor dents, and paint fading in certain areas. The interior is functional but shows its age, with worn upholstery, some scuffs on trim panels, and general signs of everyday use over the years. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though we recommend having your own mechanic inspect it prior to purchase, as there may be maintenance items that need attention. This is a practical, budget-conscious option for a buyer who understands they are getting a used vehicle with history and is comfortable with some cosmetic and potential mechanical imperfections. Priced fairly to reflect the true condition.",
      "price": 19500.0,
