      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition, and we want to be fully transparent about what you're getting. The exterior shows visible signs of wear \u2014 expect noticeable scratches, some paint fading, and a couple of small dents that are apparent upon close inspection. The interior is functional but shows its age, with worn upholstery, some scuffs on the trim panels, and general signs of regular use over the years. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some attention \u2014 we recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you can make a fully informed decision. This is a solid opportunity for a buyer who is comfortable with a project vehicle or looking for reliable basic transportation at an accessible price point. What you see is what you get, and we price accordingly.",
